author: wonpoint4
body: This data files are used by this PR. ( https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/33983# ) This PR adds a new class for a MVA based TrajectorySeed quality estimator and a new EDProducer for selecting high quality seeds for the Run 3 Muon HLT development.
title: Add MuonHLT Seed Classifier model files, Update README
